be.panako.strategy.nfft

Class NFFTFingerprint

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.panako.strategy.nfft.NFFTFingerprint

  • public class NFFTFingerprint
extends java.lang.Object
    A fingerprint connects two event points in a spectrogram. The points are defined by a time and frequency pair, both encoded with an integer. The frequency is defined by the bin index in the spectrogram. The time is defined as the index of the block processed.
    Author:
    Joren Six
